                <mxCell id="ct-step12" value="&lt;b&gt;12. Root Cause Analysis (RCA)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;font style=&#39;font-size:10px;color:#7B241C;&#39;&gt;Created off Exception where action is &amp;quot;Raise Issue&amp;quot;;&lt;br/&gt;Identify Root Cause; document 4Cs;&lt;br/&gt;Exception to RCA: many-to-many;&lt;br/&gt;Data loaded from DEA/OET workpapers&lt;br/&gt;(Control ID, Control Name, Description)&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#F1948A;strokeColor=#C0392B;fontColor=#7B241C;" parent="lane-cto" vertex="1">
