                <mxCell id="e-rd-crcc" value="" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;strokeWidth=2;strokeColor=#5B9BD5;dashed=1;exitX=0.75;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;" parent="1" source="rev-rev-details" target="crc-rev-details" edge="1">
                    <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="wf-note-ct" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&#39;font-size: 17px;&#39;&gt;Compliance Testing — Key Steps Summary&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;1. Annual Plan:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; Review Manager creates Annual Plan covering ICRM AEs, regulations, policies, GRC Risk Taxonomies; annual/quarterly planning.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;2. Review Details:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; High-level details of what the Review will test and over what time frame. CTO creates within Annual Plan.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;3. Initial Scoping:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; PF ICRM Initial Scoping Meeting; CTO documents Minute of Meetings.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;4. RAM:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; Review Announcement Memo sent to Accountable Business Executives and Stakeholders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;5. Opening Meeting:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; CTO presents Opening Meeting Deck to stakeholders, schedules via Outlook.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;6. RPD:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; Review Planning Document finalises coverage scope (AEs, Obligations, Policies, Actionable Components). Approved by Review Manager.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;7-10. RWP Execution:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; DEA (Control Design Based Testing), OET (Control Based Testing in Operation), Substantive Testing (Transaction Based). RPD to each WP is 1-to-many.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;11. Exception:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; CTO details exceptions found in RPD or any WP. Each entity to exception: 1-to-many.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;12. RCA:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; Root Cause Analysis. Exception-to-RCA: many-to-many. Approved by Review Manager.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;13. iCAPS:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; Once RCA approved, draft Issue &amp;amp; CAPs created in iCAPS. RCA-to-iCAPS: 1-to-1.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;14. Draft &amp;amp; Final Report:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; SLA: Draft Report within 7 calendar days of Execution End Date. Final Report available once all WP modules approved AND Draft Report Issuance Date entered in Review Details.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;align=left;spacingLeft=10;spacingRight=10;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="180" y="1160" width="850" height="370" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="actor-note-ct" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&#39;font-size: 17px;&#39;&gt;Actors &amp;amp; Roles&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;Review Manager:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; Creates Annual Plan; approves Review Details, RPD and RCA; issues Draft Report (7-day SLA); publishes Final Report.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;Compliance Testing Officer (CTO):&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; Creates Review Details, performs Initial Scoping, RAM, Opening Meeting, RPD, all RWP workpapers (DEA/OET/Substantive), documents Exceptions, performs RCA.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;Accountable Business Executive / Stakeholders:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; Receives RAM memo; attends Opening Meeting; provides evidence for workpaper execution; reviews Draft Report; provides management response.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;CRC-ICRM System:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; Stores Review Details, RPD and all workpapers in Testing Module; consolidates exceptions; creates iCAPS Issue &amp;amp; CAP records; stores Draft/Final Reports.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;text-align: left;&#39;&gt;&lt;b style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt;Review Director/Delegates:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-size:13px;&#39;&gt; Higher-level approval authority for RPD and Reports (where applicable per entitlements).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;fillColor=#EBF5FB;strokeColor=#2E86C1;align=left;spacingLeft=10;spacingRight=10;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="1160" y="1185" width="800" height="310" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
